<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Nobleness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Nobleness,</orth> 1) magnanimity, generosity, elevated sentiments: <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 12</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.119" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 119</bibl> (Q<hi rend="sub">1</hi> <emph>nobless</emph>). <bibl n="shak. cor 5.3.72" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 3, 72</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 5.1.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 1, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.14.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 14, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.45" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.3.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 3, 33</bibl>. <cit><quote>n. of mind,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.14" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 14</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the n. of life is to do thus,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 1.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 1, 36</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) illustrious descent, or distinguished rank: <cit><quote>regard the stamp of n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.12" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>signs of n. shall shine on all deservers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 1.4.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 4, 41</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>flatterers, foes to n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 3.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 1, 45</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thy gait did prophesy a royal n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.176" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 176</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>virtue and cunning were endowments greater than n. and riches,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 3.2.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 2, 28</bibl></cit>. With <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>n. of birth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.3.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 3, 33</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>